      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped... i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s not spraying blood or anything but it’s been oozing for a while and won't really stop. i don't really want to go to the clinic in this traffic, so i was wondering if i can just put some honey on it and bandage it up? i heard that's good for healing stuff naturally.",
