    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait 1000mg of vitamin C?? that sounds like a lot lol. is that actually gonna help it close up faster? i was really hoping to avoid the hospital if i could just treat it myself. do you think the honey + vitamin c thing would be enough to avoid needing stitches?",
